Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一(けいいち)）その… やっぱり 俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it seems like\Nsomeone's trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命を狙われているみたいです…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:11.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままいくと\N俺も 悟史(さとし)と同じ運命をたどると…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she said I'll\Nface the same fate as Satoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:16.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石(おおいし)）具体的には？\N（圭一）転校と…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）転校？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirited Away by the Demon\NChapter Four, Disturbance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When They Cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind where I looked back\N(who's there in the front)?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised my nails in the dark\N(and slashed the night).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Raindrops become droplets of\Nblood and drip down the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have\Na place to go back to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...then stop here on my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you away\Nalong with that finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To the unopenable\Nforest where cicadas cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't turn back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:03.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… すぐ戻りますから\N（大石）ああ はい かまいませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）フフッ… こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:21.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レ… レナ… 何しに来たんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, have you eaten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君 ご飯食べた？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…\N（ﾚﾅ）フフフッ… じゃ 良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お惣菜(そうざい)とか持ってきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some side dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お台所とか貸してくれれば\N温(あった)めてあげ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could warm it in the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ありがたいんだけどさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful, but it looks\Nlike dinner will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:38.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）もう少しで\N夕飯ができるみたいなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）そうなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:44.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）うちの おふくろってさ\N結構 おかずをいっぱい作るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom makes\Na lot of side dishes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから…\N（ﾚﾅ）本当に お母さん―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your mother\Nreally make dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご飯作ってくれたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… あっ いや だから…\Nくれたんじゃなくて 今…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, she didn't,\Nbut right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？\N（圭一）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてウソをつくのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かな？\N（圭一）ウソなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソだよ！\N（圭一）ウッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dinner is\Ncup ramen, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）圭一君のお夕飯\Nカップラーメンでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,豚骨しょうが味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grilled ginger pork, which\Nyou bought at Seventh Mart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買ったのはセブンスマート\N（圭一）なんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:17.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）でも それだけじゃダメだよ\Nちゃんと野菜も食べなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not enough for you.\NYou should eat vegetables too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 圭一君\Nここを開けて ねっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Keiichi-kun,\Ncould you open this please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:24.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チェーンを引く音）\N帰ってくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）圭一君 開けてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むから 帰ってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go home! Go home!\N- Ouch! It hurts, Keiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ！ 帰れ！\N（ﾚﾅ）痛い…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛いよ 圭一君… 痛い…\N（圭一）帰れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go home! Go home!\N- Ouch! It really hurts, Keiichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ！\N（ﾚﾅ）本当に痛いの 圭一君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ！\N（ﾚﾅ）悪ふざけが過ぎたなら謝るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go home! Go home!\N- I'm sorry for fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ… 帰れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）痛いの…\Nごめんなさい ごめんなさい…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go home!\N- I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ！ 帰れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい ごめんなさい…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ！ 帰れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい ごめんなさい…\N（圭一）帰れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.\N- Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:18.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし 大石さん？\N今 レナが来ました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rena was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）遊びに来たんですか？\N（圭一）いえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:26.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大石さん\N話してください レナのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san,\Nplease tell me about Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind,\Nbut don't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かまいませんが\N他言無用で お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there might be\Nsome assumptions made...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）また 内容には一部 臆測も\N含まれているかもしれませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしいですか？\N（圭一）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雷鳴）\N（大石）分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…\N（大石）正直 疑ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, I'm suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean they're suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり レナたちが犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ いや そういう意味ではなく…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“オヤシロさま”をですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Oyashiro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if Oyashiro-sama's\Ncurse really exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オヤシロさまのたたりって\N本当にあるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…な～んて まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The incident with Rena Ryugu\Nthat I told you about before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先日 お話しした竜宮(りゅうぐう)レナの事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:11.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）茨城の学校で\Nガラス窓を割って回ったっていう…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking the school\Nwindows in Ibaraki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Actually, there are victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）\Nはい　実は 被害者がいるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N（大石）それも―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, three male students she\Nwas close to were hit with a bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:21.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても親しかった男子生徒３人が\Nバットで殴られているんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バットで？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But neither the school\Nnor victims prosecuted...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:28.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに 学校側も被害者側も\N告発していないので―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事件には なっていないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...so it didn't go to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:35.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この辺りが どうも\N関係者は 皆さん 口が重い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those involved somehow are\Nnot willing to disclose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,被害者の１人は\N片目に後遺症を残すくらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Though one victim had\Na damaged eye from the beating...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:42.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴られているのにもかかわらず\N訴えるどころか―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...he didn't go to court\Nor talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,語ろうともしない\N（圭一）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）前原(まえばら)君 聞こえてますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）…言ってんだ？\N（大石）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Maebara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）何ですか？ 前原さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）“ごめんなさい”\N（大石）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maebara-san? Maebara-san?\N- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前原さん？ 前原さん？\N（圭一）“ごめんなさい”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ごめんなさい”\N（大石）もしも～し！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.\N- Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）“ごめんなさい”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音(みおん)）圭ちゃん！\N（圭一）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）おはよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭ちゃんって\N野球 好きだったっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you always like baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate!\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気が散る！ 放っといてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop swinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてよ 素振り！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:34.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何だよ？\N（魅音）やめてよ 素振り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop swinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to stop for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃなくて\N今日で終わりにしてほしいの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんでだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not bothering anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:46.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に 誰にも迷惑かけてないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）かけてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が いつ誰に迷惑かけたよ？\N（魅音）それ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did I bother and when?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even\Nsomeone else's bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人のバットだし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something\Na transfer student forgot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,転校した生徒の忘れ物だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:01.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）変わってるよな\N兄貴だけ転校して―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the brother transferred,\Nand his little sister didn't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妹は転校しなかったんだろう？\N（魅音）知ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi Hojo.\NSatoko's older brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北条(ほうじょう)悟史　沙都子(さとこ)の兄貴だろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,去年 鬼隠しに遭って消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirited away\Nlast year and vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Satoshi\Nwas also practicing swinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悟史も\Nやってたんだってな？ 素振り
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも 失踪の直前に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And right before he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）これってさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a warning for\NOyashiro-sama's curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オヤシロさまの\Nたたりに遭う前兆ってわけなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, everyone's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 怖がってるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしも これが悪ふざけなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're fooling around, then you\Nhave to stop imitating Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悟史のマネは絶対にやめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先に言っとく\N俺は 悟史のことは何も知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this first. I don't\Nknow anything about Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなが隠してたからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠してたってわけじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't hiding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖がらせたくなかったってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shut out just for that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけが理由で\N俺だけ のけ者かよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そんなつもりじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）ダム現場で\N事件がなかったかって聞いたよな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked if something\Nhappened at the dam site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）\N“ない”って言ったじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バラバラ殺人があったのによ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the dismemberment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソつき野郎が！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん　ウソってわけじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間ってのは\N隠し事なんか なしだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends don't hide things\Nfrom each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前らは仲間じゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're not my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,け… 圭ちゃん そんなのって…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:18.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ それに 見舞いのおはぎ\Nあれ うまかったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the ohagi that\Nyou gave me was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So good it made me bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血が出るくらいにな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったのは どっちだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You or Rena?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前か？ レナか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を消そうとしても\N簡単には いかないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't easily get\Nrid of me even if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悟史を消せたように\N簡単に消せると思うなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can get rid\Nof me as easily as Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が\N殺されたダム工事の現場監督と―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you\Ngot into several fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度も取っ組み合いのケンカを\Nしてたってのも知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the dam construction\Ndirector who got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠しきれると思ったのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして そんなことまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こうぜ\N授業に遅れるとマズイだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd suck if we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（泣き声）\Nひどいよ 圭ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cruel, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）そっか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who told you\Neverything was that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭ちゃんに全部バラしたの\Nあの野郎か…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've killed him back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき 殺しとくんだったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今年で定年だからって\N容赦してやった恩も忘れやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He forgot how I forgave him since\Nhe was going to retire this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:24.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…\Nちくしょう あのじじい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that old bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に殺してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Old bastard...\NYou mean Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じじいって 大石さんの…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she have a cleaver?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでナタなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Keiichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君 見ぃ～つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 何の用だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My home is the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君と同じ帰り道だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ そのナタは何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's that cleaver for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi-kun, isn't\Nsomething bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君 悩んでることが\Nあるんじゃないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:28.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖いんだよね？ 圭一君\N（圭一）アアッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖くなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）\N悟史君が転校しちゃったときは―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When Satoshi-kun transferred,\NI really regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に後悔したんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really regretted not listening\Nto what was bothering him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レナが\N相談に乗ってあげられればって―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごく後悔した
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,転校って\N鬼隠しのことなんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Transferred... You mean spirited\Naway by the demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悟史を消したのは 誰だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who got rid of Satoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you? Or Mion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レナか？ 魅音か？\Nそれとも 村の誰かか？ 答えろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it someone from\Nthe village? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言ってるのか分からないなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it so you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:03.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 分かるように言ってやる！\N連続怪死事件の犯人は 誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who committed\Nthe serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君は勘違いしてるよ\N（圭一）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間の犯人なんか いない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro-sama\Ndecides everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ては\Nオヤシロさまが決めることだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro-sama's\Ncurse is superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）オヤシロさまの\Nたたりなんて 迷信だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe\Nin Oyashiro-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）圭一君は\N信じないの？ オヤシロさま
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could\NI believe such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… 信じられるはずないだろう\Nそんなの！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro-sama does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるよ オヤシロさま\N（圭一）アア…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Has someone\Napologized to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君さ\N誰かに謝られたことない？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And for a long, long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも ずっと… ず～っと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）レナの所にも\N来たんだよ オヤシロさま
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oyashiro-sama came to me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:45.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから レナは転校して\N雛見沢(ひなみざわ)に帰ってきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I transferred and\Ncame back to Hinamizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I can listen\Nto your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君の相談に乗れるのは 私だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭一君を転校なんか させないから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:58.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 話して\N（圭一）何だよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レナが聞いてあげる\N助けてあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 話して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウ… ウソだろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:44.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンンッ！ 何か俺に用かよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit you on the foreheads\Nnext, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:48.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は眉間にお見舞いするぞ\Nこの野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When They Cry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When They Cry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should stay laid down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:10.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾚﾅ）\N横になってたほうがいいと思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）ハッ… レナ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:15.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お医者さんに電話したから\Nもうすぐ来ると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I called the doctor,\Nso he should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして ここに？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）おジャマしま～す\N（ドアの開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mion? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魅音… なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family wasn't here,\Nso I called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お家(うち)の人いなかったから\N私がね 電話したの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you look okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？ 元気そうじゃん\N心配して損したかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I waste time worrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rena, did you call the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）レナ 監督には電話した？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 魅(み)ぃちゃんに電話したあと\Nすぐ来るって言ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The director will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“監督”って 何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）アハハハッ…\N圭ちゃん 知らないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know? If I say\Ndirector, I mean the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,監督っていったら 監督だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're into baseball\Nnowadays, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭ちゃん\N最近は野球に凝ってるんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll make the director happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,監督 それ聞いたら喜ぶと思うな\N（ﾚﾅ）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 監督って誰だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハハハッ… 監督は監督さんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The director is the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 誰だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… お前ら…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）そうだ 監督が来る前に\N済ませとくかな 罰ゲーム
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish the punishment\Ngame before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罰ゲーム？\N（ﾚﾅ）おはぎの宿題…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The ohagi homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you forgot about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か 忘れてたよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アアッ… 何のマネだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is this?\N- Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動かないでね 罰ゲームだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a punishment game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ それ… 何のマネだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圭ちゃん 分かってんでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, you know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が… 何が分かってるって…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）薬物を疑いましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We suspected drugs, but we\Ncouldn't detect anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう たぐいの物は\N検出できませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンンッ！\N（魅音）ハハッ… 観念しなって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ… やめろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（殴る音）\Nハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来やがった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レナと魅音は犯人の一味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rena and Mion are suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:56.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかにも大人が４～５人以上\N白いワゴン車を所有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more than four or\Nfive adults who own a white van.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomitake-san's death\Nwas from an unknown drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,富竹(とみたけ)さんの死は\N未知の薬物によるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,証拠の注射器は これです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The proof is this syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして…\Nどうして こんなことに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（村人）いたぞ 裏口だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here! The back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刑事）少々お待ちください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Oishi-san,\Nyou have a call from the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刑事）あっ 大石さん\N一般の方から外線です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）ああ こりゃどうも\N（刑事）公衆からですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a public phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Oishi, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大石です もしもし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）お… 大石さんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前原さん？ 何かありましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san?\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:05.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ その… ウウッ…\N（大石）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何があったんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinamizawa telephone booth\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:11.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あ… あの… 俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinamizawa telephone booth\NU-U-U-Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Maebara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着いて 前原さん\N今 そこに近場の警官を行かせます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send a nearby officer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there right away too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も すぐ そっちに行きますから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's probably useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ その… 多分 ムリです\N間に合わな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one phone booth\Nthere. I sent a car. Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）落ち着いて 前原さん\N今 どういう状況なんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one phone booth\Nthere. I sent a car. Five minutes.\NCalm down, Maebara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one phone booth\Nthere. I sent a car. Five minutes.\NHow's the situation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the situation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too long! How many\Npeople are in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かかりすぎです！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,警邏(けいら)には何人乗ってます？\N（刑事）２人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call the resident officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）\N雛見沢の駐在さんに電話は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,定時巡回の時間で 不在です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on scheduled patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma-chan,\Nplease prepare a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熊(くま)ちゃん 車を回してください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（熊谷(くまがい)）了解ッス！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし 前原さん\N今そこに警官が向かってます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Maebara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an officer\Nheaded there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２～３分で到着しますから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be two to three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san,\Nwho's the suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前原さん\N犯人は誰です？ 何人なんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）お… 俺も 最初は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I also thought at first that\Nthe suspect was human...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間が犯人なんだと思いまし…\Nウウッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Oyashiro-sama seems to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オヤシロさまってのは\Nいるんだと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right now...\N- Maebara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今…\N（大石）前原さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:15.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウウッ…\Nず～っと つけてくるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps following me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I run,\Nrun, run, and run...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走っても走っても\N走っても走っても…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...it sticks to me like a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,影みたいに ぴったり くっついて…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Little by little, little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ… 少しずつ 俺の背中に\Nにじり寄ってくるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...it keeps coming\Ncloser to my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（せきこみ）\N（大石）前原さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san, is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:35.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは今 ひょっとして\N前原さんの…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,\Nby any chance, is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろに… すぐ後ろに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me... Right behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァハァ…\N（大石）誰がいるんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振り向けるわけないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I look back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振り向いたら 俺… 俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I turn around, I'II... I'II...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're afraid!\NBut I want you to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖いのは分かります\Nでも 教えてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turn around a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと振り返るだけでいいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's behind you,\NMaebara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:59.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前原さんの後ろに\N誰が… 誰がいるんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maebara-san, you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前原さん あんた まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アアッ…\N（大石）喉を―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...clawing your throat, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひっかいたりしては\Nいないでしょうね？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:11.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アアッ…\N（大石）もしもし 前原さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Maebara-san? Maebara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前原…\N（圭一）ご… な… い…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san, the car is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（熊谷）大石さん 車 ＯＫッス！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（熊谷）大石さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ごめんなさい”だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,June 1983
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Report
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In Shishibone City, Hinamizawa,\Nfemale students were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大石）鹿骨(ししぼね)市雛見沢で\N女子生徒殺人事件が発生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,容疑者は前原圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect is Keiichi Maebara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Inviting over two classmates,\NRena Ryugu and Mion Sonozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:45.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自宅にクラスメートの女子２名―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜宮レナ 園崎(そのざき)魅音を呼び寄せ\N金属バットで撲殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...he beat them\Nto death with a bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He fled and was found collapsed\Nin a phone booth by officers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,容疑者は犯行現場から逃走後―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:58.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,警邏中の警察官に電話ボックス内で\N倒れているのを発見されるも―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...dying 24 hours\Nlater at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,24時間後に収容先の病院にて死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,検視の結果\N死因は出血性ショック死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The autopsy said death was\Ncaused by shock from blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自らの爪で喉を引き裂き―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By slitting his throat\Nwith his own nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その結果\N出血多量で死に至ったもよう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...he died from\Nlosing too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of drugs was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,薬物などの使用は認められず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シャッター音）\N（大石）その後 容疑者の自室から
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, a handwritten memo was\Nfound in the suspect's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直筆のメモが発見される
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メモはＢ５の大学ノートを\N半分に裂いた物２枚で構成され
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made of two sheets of B5\Ncollege-ruled paper cut in half...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...and taped behind\Nthe clock on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壁の時計の裏に貼り付けられていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That memo must've\Noriginally been one B5 page...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのメモは 元は\NＢ５のページに書かれた物を―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...which was torn to remove a few\Nlines in the middle of the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者かが\N真ん中の数行を削除するために―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破り捨てたのではないかと\N推測される
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From the large amount of tape\Nresidue behind the clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:43.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また 時計裏に付着していた\N大量の粘着テープ跡から―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メモ以外にも何かが\N貼り付けられていたのではないかと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...it could be assumed that\Nsomething else was also taped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以下が そのメモの内容である
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The following is the memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“私 前原圭一は\N命を狙われています”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Keiichi Maebara,\Nam in danger of getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:04.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“なぜ 誰に命を\N狙われているのかは分かりません”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why or who.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ただひとつ分かることは―”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“オヤシロさまのたたりと\N関係があるということです”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...is that it has something to do\Nwith Oyashiro-sama's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rena and Mion are suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“レナと魅音は犯人の一味”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more than four or\Nfive adults who own a white van.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:17.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ほかにも大人が４～５人以上\N白いワゴン車を所有”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The following is the second page.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以下は２枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“どうして\Nこんなことになったのか―”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how things\Nturned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“私には分かりません”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（圭一）\Nこれを あなたが読んだなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably be dead by\Nthe time you read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:31.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき 私は死んでいるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To the one reading this,\Nplease uncover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:36.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを読んだ あなた\Nどうか真相を暴いてください
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my only wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけが私の望みです\N前原圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiichi Maebara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To get my happiness,\NI had done everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...but had done nothing\Nto be blamed and accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of footsteps\Nbecame louder every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I noticed the fact\Nthere was no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a believer in life,\Nto be myself always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And was asking\Nwhether I would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a reason\Nwhy not to adopt in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or judge me to be guilty\Nof so many incurable sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me why or why not?\NComplaining way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.85,0:23:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I overlooked\Nsomething fatal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Preview\NI want you to stare at the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N見つめてほしい 本当の自分を…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to forgive\Nthe whimsical you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:23.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許してほしい\N気まぐれな あなたを…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってほしい もう１人の私を…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you\Nto understand the other me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「ひぐらしのなく頃に」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When They Cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cotton Drifting\NChapter One, Jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cotton Drifting\NChapter One, Jealousy\NThe Cotton Drifting\NChapter One, Jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは信じられますか？
